---Basic Auth---

https://www.base64encode.org/ to encode admin:admin or tan:Pass123

Open thunderclient

get http://127.0.0.1:8000/endpoint1

go to headers

add Authorization: Basic B64code

send

---Jwt Auth--- 

Open thunderclient

post http://127.0.0.1:8000/token

body -> Form-encode

add username: admin or johndoe
add password: admin123 or secret

send -> kuha si token

change to get http://127.0.0.1:8000/secure-data or normal-data

go to header

Authorization: Bearer tokencode

send
